      "blocks": {
        "text_Rbh9fn": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The next chapter of my life took me to New York, a city just as captivating and vibrant as any place I had ever experienced.</p><p>At every cross-street, I discovered a new direction. With every bridge I crossed, I built new connections. And in every gallery, I reflected on my personal canvas.</p><p>After a Masters' degree from NYU, I spent over a decade working with large American and European personal-care, consumer and wellness  companies on strategy and product innovation - advising them on new ways to create and grow. If there's one thing I learned from my experience as a global strategy consultant, it's that breakthroughs come from re-imagining possibilities.</p>",
            "text_size": "typeset",
            "secondary_color": true
          }
        }
      },
