      "blocks": {
        "text_VApDhT": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At about the same time, I saw some of the basic customs and ingredients I had grown up with (coconut oil, turmeric etc.) make their way into the fabric of everyday food and wellness in the US and other Western markets. However, I also knew that these early, tentative crossovers barely scraped the surface of the well-guarded riches and rituals the varied regions of the Indian sub-continent had to offer. </p><p>I knew then, that I had to find a way to take these incredible subcontinental ingredients & customs that I was intimately familiar with, leverage my background in innovation, and apply the best technology New York has to offer - to create potent potions.</p>",
            "text_size": "typeset",
            "secondary_color": true
          }
        }
